er\nconstant-factor approximations to the pre-selection problem. Detailed\nevaluations reveal that the proposed algorithms and their enhancements offer\nsignificant gains.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 18 Jan 2012 18:13:36 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 12 Apr 2012 16:27:02 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 29 Nov 2013 20:06:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-12-02"}
